<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She did her first ever Instagram Live session the day before to encourage her followers to register to vote.</p>

<p>And Kendall Jenner kept her message consistent as she stepped out in Malibu on Wednesday with a black mask reading, 'VOTE.'</p>

<p>The 24-year-old Keeping Up With The Kardashians star made the political statement while stopping to pick up some purple smoothies. </p>

